### Workout Tracker API - HTTP Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@aiCoachUrl = http://localhost:8001

### ============ WORKOUT API ============

### Health Check / Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Get All Exercises
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises

###

### Get Exercise by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/exercises/1

###

### Create New Exercise (Weighted)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bench Press",
  "sets": 4,
  "reps": 8,
  "weight": 80.0
}

###

### Create Bodyweight Exercise (No Weight)
POST {{baseUrl}}/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pull-ups",
  "sets": 3,
  "reps": 10
}

###

### Update Exercise (Partial - Change Weight)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/exercises/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weight": 85.0
}

###

### Update Exercise (Partial - Change Sets and Reps)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/exercises/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sets": 5,
  "reps": 6
}

###

### Delete Exercise
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/exercises/1

### ============ AI COACH API ============

### AI Coach Health Check
GET {{aiCoachUrl}}/health

###

### Chat with AI Coach (with workout context)
POST {{aiCoachUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What exercises should I add for a more balanced routine?",
  "include_workout_context": true
}

###

### Chat with AI Coach (general question)
POST {{aiCoachUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What's the best way to warm up before weightlifting?",
  "include_workout_context": false
}

###

### Get Workout Recommendation - Back Focus
POST {{aiCoachUrl}}/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "focus_area": "back",
  "session_duration_minutes": 45,
  "equipment_available": ["barbell", "dumbbells", "cables", "pull-up bar"]
}

###

### Get Workout Recommendation - Chest Focus
POST {{aiCoachUrl}}/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "focus_area": "chest",
  "session_duration_minutes": 60,
  "equipment_available": ["barbell", "dumbbells", "cables", "bench"]
}

###

### Get Workout Recommendation - Full Body
POST {{aiCoachUrl}}/recommend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_duration_minutes": 60
}

###

### Analyze Current Workout Routine
GET {{aiCoachUrl}}/analyze

###

### Get Exercises (Proxy through AI Coach)
GET {{aiCoachUrl}}/exercises

### ============ AUTHENTICATION ============

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Login as regular user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### Get current user info (requires token)
# Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login response
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### List all users (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Admin delete exercise (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/exercises/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

